Class DangerMovement

  • java.lang.Object
    • movement.MovementModel
      • movement.ExtendedMovementModel
        • movement.DangerMovement

  • public class DangerMovement
extends ExtendedMovementModel
    This movement model makes use of several other movement models to simulate movement in crisis situation.
